Article.ArticleTitle: Two new cephalochromin derivative from the Alternaria sp. ZG22.

AbstractText: Two new cephalochromin derivatives, prenylcephalochromin A (1), prenylcephalochromin B (2), along with cephalochromin (3) were isolated from the Alternaria sp. ZG22 obtained from a Dasymaschalon rostratum collected from the Hainan. The structures of two new compounds were elucidated by comprehensive spectroscopic methods. Compounds 1-3 showed α-glucosidase inhibitory activity.
